      "raw_text": "BUTTE. Dec. 17.-According to\nBoston reports the closing down of\nthe Anaconda group of mines and\nthe Washoe smelter at Anaconda\nby the Amalgamated Copper Co.. is\nfor the purpose of reducing wages\nand establishing the open shop\" in\nthe Butte mines. The story does\nnot receive much credence in\nButte"
